description: Creates a bulk thing provisioning task. Requires permission to access the StartThingRegistrationTask action.

parameters.name: inputFileBucket
parameters.description: The S3 bucket that contains the input file.

parameters.name: inputFileKey
parameters.description: The name of input file within the S3 bucket. This file contains a newline delimited JSON file. Each line contains the parameter values to provision one device (thing).

parameters.name: roleArn
parameters.description: The IAM role ARN that grants permission the input file.

nested_items.name: taskId
nested_items.description: The bulk thing provisioning task ID.
